8:
Yahweh acts mercifully and kindly;\q2 he does not quickly get angry when we sin;
\q1 he is always showing us that he faithfully loves us.


\q1

15:
We humans do not live forever;\q2 we are like grass which withers and dies.
\q1 We are like wild flowers that bloom for a short while;
\q1

17:
But Yahweh will faithfully keep loving forever\q2 all those who revere him, as he promised.
\q2 He will act fairly to our children and to their children;
\q1

20:
You angels who belong to Yahweh, praise him!\q2 You are powerful creatures who do what he tells you to do;
\q2 you obey what he commands.
\q1
